Ellie Grant was appearing on ITV's This Morning to discuss how she suddenly developed Tourette's syndrome . 
  She was discussing how she found love with fiance Jordan - who is deaf and switches off his hearing aid when she gets rowdy . 
  But in the middle of the interview she suddenly blurted out 'silver fox' at Phillip Schofield . 
  Silver fox is the nickname of the father-of-two - who looked bemused and embarrassed at the comment . 
  Miss Grant, 22, was appearing to talk about how she developed the condition . 
 